<div id="review_670101345" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/670101345" />
    <a title="Kathryn" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/2600090-kathryn"><img alt="Kathryn" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1616875828p2/2600090.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/670101345?book_show_action=true">Jul 17, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kathryn" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kathryn" href="/user/show/2600090-kathryn">Kathryn</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2600090-kathryn?shelf=2017">2017</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer670101345" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1868368557341540771">This book is just captivating. It has been on my to-read list a very long time and I now I look forward to reading more by <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/3501.Kaye_Gibbons' title='Kaye Gibbons' rel='nofollow noopener'>Kaye Gibbons</a>. This story surrounds the lives of a grandmother, her daughter, and her granddaughter. Each was fascinating in their day-to-day lives and the dynamics of their family was humorous and heartwarming.<br/><br/>I loved the quote on the back from Time Magazine: &quot;Graceful and spirited....As invigorating as sarsaparilla and as soothing as lemon-balm tea.&quot;</span>
  <span id="freeText1868368557341540771" style="display:none">This book is just captivating. It has been on my to-read list a very long time and I now I look forward to reading more by <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/3501.Kaye_Gibbons" title="Kaye Gibbons" rel="nofollow noopener">Kaye Gibbons</a>. This story surrounds the lives of a grandmother, her daughter, and her granddaughter. Each was fascinating in their day-to-day lives and the dynamics of their family was humorous and heartwarming.<br /><br />I loved the quote on the back from Time Magazine: "Graceful and spirited....As invigorating as sarsaparilla and as soothing as lemon-balm tea."</span>
