<span id="freeTextContainer5445953266343258932">I really liked this author. I love the tone she uses in telling her story. The characters are warm and dimensional and quirky. The author also has a wonderful sense of humor. She tells the story of three generations of women at the turn of the century up until about 1945. They are intelligent and feisty and the theme of country doctor/herbalist is fascinating. Truly charming. I will definitely read more from this author.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


