              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9780547745978303060">I loved how this book was written and found myself looking forward to reading it each night. I loved the female bonds and struggles it shared in a 3 generation family. It was a quick read that made me smile with its humor.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


